extends layout

block pageTitle
  title How Shopping Works — Hedge Wears

block metaDesc
  meta(name='description' content='Free to browse. Earn HedgeCoin on every order. Redeem for discounts. Shopping on Hedge Wears is rewarding by design.')

block content

  //- ─── PAGE HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.page-hero.section
    .container
      .page-hero-inner.page-hero-inner--centered
        span.section-eyebrow Simple by design
        h1.page-hero-title Free to browse. Rewarding to buy.
        p.page-hero-subtitle No subscriptions. No hidden fees. Just fashion — and HedgeCoin on every order.

  //- ─── HOW IT WORKS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.how-it-works.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow The experience
        h2.section-title How it works
      .how-steps-grid
        .how-step
          .how-step-number 01
          h3.how-step-title Browse &amp; Discover
          p.how-step-desc Explore curated collections across clothing, footwear, and accessories. All pieces are rooted in African heritage and designed to last. No cost to browse.
        .how-step
          .how-step-number 02
          h3.how-step-title Buy with Confidence
          p.how-step-desc Pay securely through Paystack by card or bank transfer. Prices are shown in HedgeCoin (HGC) with an equivalent in your local currency for reference.
        .how-step
          .how-step-number 03
          h3.how-step-title Earn HedgeCoin
          p.how-step-desc Every completed order earns HGC automatically. Your balance grows with every purchase and never expires while your account is active.
        .how-step
          .how-step-number 04
          h3.how-step-title Redeem for Discounts
          p.how-step-desc At checkout, apply your HGC balance to reduce the cost of your order. The more you shop, the more you save &mdash; compounding loyalty, every time.

  //- ─── SHOPPER FEATURES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.shopper-features.section.section--muted
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow Everything included
        h2.section-title What you get as a customer
      .shopper-features-grid
        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title Free to Browse
          p.shopper-feature-desc No account required to explore collections. Create a free account to purchase, save favourites, and earn HGC.

        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              circle(cx='12' cy='12' r='9' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8')
              path(d='M12 7v1m0 8v1M9.5 9.5C9.5 8.67 10.67 8 12 8s2.5.67 2.5 1.5S13.33 11 12 11s-2.5.83-2.5 1.5S10.67 15 12 15s2.5-.67 2.5-1.5' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title HGC on Every Order
          p.shopper-feature-desc HedgeCoin is earned automatically on every completed purchase. No manual redemptions required — it just adds up.

        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8')
              path(d='M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title Multi-Currency Display
          p.shopper-feature-desc View prices in your local currency alongside HGC. Choose your preferred currency from settings — fully supported in the app and web shop.

        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.4 2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.22h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.8a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l.95-.95a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 16l.42.92z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title Order Tracking &amp; Notifications
          p.shopper-feature-desc Track every order from placement to delivery. Receive push notifications at each stage so you always know where your purchase is.

        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              rect(x='2' y='3' width='20' height='14' rx='2' ry='2' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
              path(d='M8 21h8M12 17v4' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title Shop on Any Device
          p.shopper-feature-desc Full experience on web and mobile. Download the iOS or Android app for the best shopping and HGC management experience on the go.

        .shopper-feature-card
          .shopper-feature-icon
            svg(width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.shopper-feature-title Secure Payments
          p.shopper-feature-desc All payments are processed by Paystack &mdash; one of Africa&rsquo;s most trusted payment processors. Your card details are never stored on Hedge Wears servers.

  //- ─── HGC CALLOUT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.pricing-note.section.section--dark
    .container
      .pricing-note-inner
        .pricing-note-icon
          img.hgc-icon-card-header(src='/img/hgc-icon.svg' alt='HGC')
        .pricing-note-text
          h3.pricing-note-title All prices in HedgeCoin (HGC)
          p.pricing-note-desc Product prices on Hedge Wears are displayed in HGC &mdash; our loyalty currency. HGC is not a cryptocurrency; it is an in-platform token that rewards every purchase. Your local currency equivalent is always shown alongside for reference.

  //- ─── FAQ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.faq.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow Got questions?
        h2.section-title Frequently asked
      .faq-list
        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question What is HedgeCoin (HGC)?
          p.faq-answer HGC is Hedge Wears&rsquo; in-app loyalty currency. You earn HGC automatically on every completed purchase and can redeem it at checkout to reduce the cost of future orders. HGC does not expire while your account is active and has no cash value.

        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question How do I earn HGC?
          p.faq-answer Simply complete a purchase on Hedge Wears &mdash; on web or mobile. HGC is credited to your wallet automatically once the order is confirmed. No codes, no sign-ups, no effort required.

        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question Does my HGC expire?
          p.faq-answer No. Your HGC balance never expires as long as your account remains active. If you close your account, any remaining HGC balance will be forfeited.

        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question What payment methods are accepted?
          p.faq-answer All payments are processed through Paystack. You can pay by debit card, credit card, or bank transfer. Your card details are never stored on Hedge Wears servers.

        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question How do returns work?
          p.faq-answer Return and refund requests are handled through our support team. Contact us at hello@hedgewears.com with your order number and we will assist you promptly.

        .faq-item
          h3.faq-question Is shopping on Hedge Wears free?
          p.faq-answer Yes. There are no subscription fees, membership fees, or browsing fees. Creating an account and purchasing is completely free. You only pay for the products you buy.

  //- ─── CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.cta-banner.section
    .container
      .cta-banner-inner
        h2.cta-banner-title Ready to start earning HGC?
        p.cta-banner-subtitle Every purchase builds your balance. Start shopping and let your loyalty compound.
        .cta-banner-actions
          a.btn.btn-white.btn-lg(href=webShopUrl target='_blank' rel='noopener') Shop Now
          a.btn.btn-outline-white.btn-lg(href='/download') Download App
